WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
&lt;h2&gt;Iran War — Day 29&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Houthis entered the war, launching

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
ballistic missiles at Israel — their first strike since the

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Hamas ceasefire. At least 10 US service members were injured

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
in an Iranian attack on Prince Sultan Air Base. Brent

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
crude hit $112.57, up 4.2%. Reddit surfaced a WSJ report

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
that the US may deploy up to 17,000 troops near

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Iran. The UK’s Starmer reaffirmed Britain will not join.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;DHS Shutdown

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
— Day 43&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Senate passed a bipartisan funding bill, then

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:36.000
the House rejected it and passed their own (213-203), which

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Senate Democrats called dead on arrival. Both chambers left for

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
a two-week recess. 61,000+ TSA workers have missed three paychecks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Anthropic

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
v. Pentagon&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Judge Lin’s preliminary injunction stands. Government appeal deadline is

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Thursday, April 2 — the same day as Jacob’s Anthropic

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
pilot discussion at work.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Tech &amp;amp; AI&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Semafor: A 19-year-old’s AI agent

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
team spent £1,426 on unauthorized catering. Stratechery: RIP Sora, OpenAI

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
killed it for GPUs. Kash Patel’s email was hacked. SoftBank

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
taking a $40B loan for OpenAI (IPO signal). WA bans

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
non-compete agreements.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Apple&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Apple turns 50 on Wednesday. No iPhone in Lockdown

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.000
Mode has ever been hacked. The C1X modem matches Qualcomm

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
on speed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Calendar&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Monday: Ben arrives. Tuesday: Payday + carpet install. Wednesday:

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
Q2 starts, Karen retirement announcement, Apple 50th. Thursday: Anthropic pilot

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
9AM, dinner with friends 6PM, government appeal deadline.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;From Reddit&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;r/Tacoma: Cherry

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.000
blossoms at Wapato Hills, No Kings protest today. r/SeattleWA: WA

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.000
bans non-competes, Seattle police starting pay ~$118K. r/apple: Lockdown Mode

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.800
undefeated, Apple hiring Google VP for AI.&lt;/p&gt;
